# Source maps — generated only in CI when SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN is set.
# The sentryVitePlugin deletes them after upload (filesToDeleteAfterUpload).
# This entry is a safety net so .map files never reach the repo even if
# the plugin fails to delete them.
*.map

